# Radio-Streamer

You need:

1) Debian 13 without GUI: https://www.debian.org or if you're building it on a Raspberry Pi: https://www.raspberrypi.com
   
2) BalenaEtcher (https://www.balena.io/etcher) or 'dd command' to create a bootable USB:
    $diskutil list
    $diskutil umountDisk /dev/diskXX
    $sudo dd bs=1m if=YOUR_DEBIAN_IMAGE.img of=/dev/diskXX

4) Wi-Fi antenna (if your computer/Raspberry Pi doesn't have one, and want to use this interface): 

5) Bluetooth antenna (if your computer/Raspberry Pi doesn't have one, and want to use this interface): 

6) USB stick (for Raspberry Pi only): https://a.co/d/9WlAjas

7) Shutdown button (for Raspberry Pi only): Micro USB: https://a.co/d/9Fj24Pe or USB C: https://a.co/d/g3vTr5e


